          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1902-Step-5-v2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>,<strong> remaining cracked black pepper</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>black pepper sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
